The way i do the Por15 is i sand the surface to get most of rust and =
paint
out, then i clean very well with marine clean, two time if possible =
then i
apply por15,  metal ready help but, i used it at first but now i =
dont... if
the area is exposed you have to put a  primer over it because por15 is
sensible to UV

and im real happy with Por15, i wonder why i didnt sed it before!!

mike
